.: Plot :.

Monzo,a crime novels writer, wants to help his friend Yurie finding Michiko:her missing step-daughter. He brings the case to Akechi,a private detective,who's occupied solving the dancer Ranko Mizuki missing case.
Monzo tells Akechi that he was present on her last show and that he saw a suspicious blind man among the public.In addition on the way back home he saw a dwarf carrying a woman's arm.
So they start investigating on the Blind Beast and the Dwarf.

